repair.repairedDockerfile:
FROM golang:1.18 AS builder

WORKDIR /go/src/github.com/whywaita/myshoes

RUN go install google.golang.org/protobuf/cmd/protoc-gen-go@latest
RUN go install google.golang.org/grpc/cmd/protoc-gen-go-grpc@latest
RUN apt-get update -y \
    && apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y protobuf-compiler && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*;

ENV CGO_ENABLED=0
ENV GOOS=linux
ENV GOARCH=amd64

COPY . .
RUN make build-linux

FROM alpine

RUN apk update \
  && apk update
RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates \
  && update-ca-certificates 2>/dev/null || true

COPY --from=builder /go/src/github.com/whywaita/myshoes/myshoes-linux-amd64 /app

CMD ["/app"]
